OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe far south mostly fading to leave a
OL,7,Flargely dry night with clear spells
OL,8,Fand variable cloud. Winds steadily
OL,9,Feasing. A warm night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FFurther showers and the odd
OL,12,Fthunderstorm could fringe the far
OL,13,Fsouth. Many others remaining dry with
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells and feeling hot
OL,15,Fwhere these are prolonged in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
